PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781698292
OL,3,CBurrows denies 'grubby deal' to block
OL,4,Cincrease to age of criminal
OL,5,Cresponsibility
OL,7,FMLAs debated an amendment to raise the
OL,8,Fage of criminal responsibility from 10
OL,9,Fto 14 as part of the Assembly passage
OL,10,Fof the Justice Bill.
OL,12,FAlliance MLA Sian Mulholland proposed
OL,13,Fthe amendment to the Bill, which would
OL,14,Fhave raised the age to 14 for most
OL,15,Foffences, with the age set at 12 for
OL,16,Fthe most serious offences of murder,
OL,17,Fmanslaughter and rape.
OL,19,FIt emerged on Monday night that enough
OL,20,Funionist MLAs had signed what is known
OL,21,Fas a petition of concern.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781698292
OL,3,CBurrows denies 'grubby deal' to block
OL,4,Cincrease to age of criminal
OL,5,Cresponsibility
OL,7,FA valid petition of concern means that
OL,8,Fthe vote on the proposal will have to
OL,9,Fbe backed by a majority of unionists
OL,10,Fand a majority of nationalists in
OL,11,Forder for it to pass, rather than a
OL,12,Fstraight majority.
OL,14,FThis means the change is set to be
OL,15,Frejected when the vote takes place, as
OL,16,Fa majority of unionists have already
OL,17,Fsigned the petition of concern in
OL,18,Fopposition to the proposal.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781698292
OL,3,CBurrows denies 'grubby deal' to block
OL,4,Cincrease to age of criminal
OL,5,Cresponsibility
OL,7,FThe petition, which requires the
OL,8,Fbacking of 30 members, was signed by
OL,9,FDUP and TUV MLAs and four Ulster
OL,10,FUnionists.
OL,12,FUntil Monday night, it had been
OL,13,Funclear whether enough UUP MLAs would
OL,14,Fsign it, as the party had been divided
OL,15,Fon whether it was appropriate to use a
OL,16,Fpetition of concern in such
OL,17,Fcircumstances.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781698292
OL,3,CBurrows denies 'grubby deal' to block
OL,4,Cincrease to age of criminal
OL,5,Cresponsibility
OL,7,FThe petition is a peace process
OL,8,Fconstruct designed to protect minority
OL,9,Frights in Northern Ireland's divided
OL,10,Fcommunity.
OL,12,FOther politicians have criticised
OL,13,Fthose who signed the petition on the
OL,14,Fvote on the age of criminal
OL,15,Fresponsibility, saying it was a misuse
OL,16,Fof the mechanism as it was nothing to
OL,17,Fdo with minority rights.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
