PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781698292
OL,3,CBurrows denies 'grubby deal' to block
OL,4,Cincrease to age of criminal
OL,5,Cresponsibility
OL,7,FWhile UUP leader Jon Burrows and
OL,8,Fdeputy leader Diana Armstrong had
OL,9,Fagreed to sign the petition of
OL,10,Fconcern, it had been unclear whether
OL,11,Fany of their party colleagues would
OL,12,Fjoin them to take the number of
OL,13,Fsignatures to the required threshold
OL,14,Fof 30.
OL,16,FIt emerged during the debate in the
OL,17,FAssembly that UUP MLAs Alan Chambers
OL,18,Fand Robbie Butler had also signed the
OL,19,Fpetition to reach the required 30
OL,20,Fsignatures.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
