PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781698292
OL,3,CBurrows denies 'grubby deal' to block
OL,4,Cincrease to age of criminal
OL,5,Cresponsibility
OL,7,FUUP leader Jon Burrows rejected
OL,8,Fsuggestions from rival politicians
OL,9,Fthat he had made a "grubby deal" with
OL,10,Feither the DUP or his own party
OL,11,Fcolleagues to ensure enough UUP MLAs
OL,12,Fsigned the petition of concern.
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, he said the legislation
OL,15,Fwas "dangerous and ill-conceived".
OL,26,@qD@TOUqD@`O]wD@EOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781698292
OL,3,CBurrows denies 'grubby deal' to block
OL,4,Cincrease to age of criminal
OL,5,Cresponsibility
OL,7,F"That legislation would go contrary to
OL,8,Feverything I believe in about putting
OL,9,Fvictims and public protection first at
OL,10,Fa time when women and girls in our
OL,11,Fsociety are facing grave threats,
OL,12,Fharassment, sexual abuse, this would
OL,13,Fhave legalised almost all of that
OL,14,Fbehaviour for anyone under the age of
OL,15,F14," he told reporters at Parliament
OL,16,FBuildings.
OL,18,F"It's the wrong signal to send to our
OL,19,Fsociety and it was profoundly
OL,20,Fdangerous.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@DO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781698292
OL,3,CBurrows denies 'grubby deal' to block
OL,4,Cincrease to age of criminal
OL,5,Cresponsibility
OL,7,F"We used the petition of concern to
OL,8,Fstop that. That is a legitimate
OL,9,Fdemocratic lever which should only be
OL,10,Fused in extremis and that is why we
OL,11,Fused it last night."
OL,13,FMr Burrows denied there had been any
OL,14,F"inducements or threats" to convince
OL,15,Fenough UUP MLAs to back the petition
OL,16,Fof concern.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@TO]vD@AOUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781698292
OL,3,CBurrows denies 'grubby deal' to block
OL,4,Cincrease to age of criminal
OL,5,Cresponsibility
OL,7,F"I do my politics with honour, I made
OL,8,Fthe case very strongly as to why this
OL,9,Fwas dangerous law, we got the four
OL,10,Fsignatures we needed and the petition
OL,11,Fof concern went through," he said.
OL,13,F"There were no deals, no threats and
OL,14,Fno inducements."
OL,16,FEngland, Wales and Northern Ireland,
OL,17,Falongside Switzerland share the lowest
OL,18,Fminimum age of criminal responsibility
OL,19,Fin Europe at 10.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@YO]uD@AOUvD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
